OL,11,G0135FDawn Chorus: The Sounds of Spring
OL,12,     GUninterrupted and unspoiled by
OL,13,     Gvoiceover or music, the birdsong
OL,14,     Gof sunrise in all its glory.
OL,15,     GThree different habitats,
OL,16,     GBritain's woodland, heathland and
OL,17,     Gparkland, burst into song.
